Fischer Weighs Further Moves Against Speculators, Calcalist Says

-- B y   A l i s a   O d e n h e i m e r
-- 
2011-03-23T10:13:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/fischer-weighs-further-moves-against-speculators-calcalist-says.html
Bank of Israel Governor  Stanley
Fischer  is weighing further rule changes to deter speculators in
the foreign  currency market , Calcalist reported, without saying
where it got the information.  Bank of Israel spokesman Yossi Saadon said in an e-mailed
response to the report that to the best of his knowledge there
is nothing new on the topic.        Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
